  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[End of Your Turn] Delete this Digimon and \uFF1CDraw 2\uFF1E.
    Then, you may return 1 [Loogamon] from your trash to the hand. [On Deletion]
    You may trash up to 3 cards with the [Dark Animal] or [SoC] trait in your hand.
    Then, delete 1 of your opponent's level 3 or lower Digimon. For each card trashed
    by this effect, add 1 to the level this effect may choose."
